	<center>
		<h1>Introduction</h1>
		<hr>
	</center>
	<p>
		User coversations in the virtual classroom are valuable resources.  They
		provide information that can be used for many other e-learning approaches.
		Currently coversations are stored in a saved transcript.  Using a relational
		index and a full text indexer we can create a queryable system that
		can be used to provide useful searching features to the user.
	</p>
